title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
